pageProps.body:
Welcome to Trevor Sullivan's technology notes!

Hello, my name is Trevor Sullivan. This is an informational site to help people with technology. You can find me on GitHub as well, where I've authored several open source projects. I also have a YouTube channel where I publish videos about technical topics, such as PowerShell, AWS, Azure, and more.

My Interests

  • Software
  • Photography / video
  • Motorcycles
  • Firearms
  • Investing
  • Hiking
  • Beer
Children
  1. Cloud
  2. Kubernetes
